{
 "name": "RPlog_Paul_Nighman_s_Letter",
 "title": "Paul Nighman's Letter",
 "summary": "In the spare barracks on Mon Calamari, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios receives a farewell letter from Paul Nighman, delivered amid the quiet company of the anxious young Shenner, Luke Skywalker, and the General Skeezix Calhoun. Visibly shaken, her hands trembling, Jessalyn tucks the envelope away with the bittersweet air of someone who half-expected the parting. Shenner hovers protectively, checking on her, while the tactful General slips out so as not to intrude on the private moment. The scene captures the ache of an unspoken goodbye and the gentle support of those around Jessalyn.",
